Requires:
kdebase4-workspace-devel, its prerequisites
NetworkManager-devel
QtNetworkManager-devel (aka libnm-qt)
QtModemManager-devel (aka libmm-qt)
glib2-devel

NetworkManager specification:

http://projects.gnome.org/NetworkManager/developers/api/09/spec.html
http://projects.gnome.org/NetworkManager/developers/api/09/ref-settings.html
